::Cygnus::
    He is following the beacon when he comes to a mountain.  He circles the 
mountain for a while looking for the base that must be there.  On his third 
pass he spots the base and heads down to land.  He lands outside the base but 
it seemed empty so he just sat down and relaxed for a while.
